1. Allow the system to be controlled by the maximum of 10 people
2. The system must be protected from all kind of viruses and attempts from unregistered members.
3. The system should be available 24 hours 7 days a week (24/7)
4. System administrator can edit the buses' information.
5. Normal users(customers) can not access buses reports unless permission is given to that specific user.
6. The system should be able to integrate with the existing systems.
7. The interactions between the user and the system must not exceed 3 seconds.
8. The system should be accessed responsively across the devices.
9. The system should provide easy ticket reservation environment for user with self-directed
10. The system should have user friendly interfaces to navigate through the system easily
 
